<codeline><highlight class="normal">#<sp/>TextVisualizer<sp/>Development<sp/>Statistics</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">##<sp/>1.<sp/>기준</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">이<sp/>문서는<sp/>`devel_text_visualizer`<sp/>브랜치에서<sp/>TextVisualizer<sp/>관련<sp/>작업이<sp/>어느<sp/>정도<sp/>누적되었는지<sp/>정리한다.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">통계<sp/>기준은<sp/>다음과<sp/>같다.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">|<sp/>항목<sp/>|<sp/>값<sp/>|</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">|---|---|</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">|<sp/>브랜치<sp/>|<sp/>`devel_text_visualizer`<sp/>|</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">|<sp/>시작<sp/>커밋<sp/>|<sp/>`9970ed2009b9650167398ba5fc935a6d94a84f1f`<sp/>|</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">|<sp/>시작<sp/>커밋<sp/>제목<sp/>|<sp/>`docs:<sp/>add<sp/>text<sp/>visualizer<sp/>overview<sp/>and<sp/>pipeline<sp/>analysis`<sp/>|</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">|<sp/>통계<sp/>산출<sp/>시점<sp/>최신<sp/>구현<sp/>커밋<sp/>|<sp/>`82f4977551c0034412faf9f17f205f107b73d57a`<sp/>|</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">|<sp/>통계<sp/>산출<sp/>시점<sp/>최신<sp/>구현<sp/>커밋<sp/>제목<sp/>|<sp/>`Design<sp/>shared<sp/>glyph<sp/>cache<sp/>helper<sp/>for<sp/>TextVisualizerGlyphRenderer`<sp/>|</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">|<sp/>커밋<sp/>범위<sp/>|<sp/>`9970ed2009b9650167398ba5fc935a6d94a84f1f^..82f4977551c0034412faf9f17f205f107b73d57a`<sp/>|</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">시작<sp/>커밋도<sp/>TextVisualizer<sp/>문서<sp/>작업이므로,<sp/>기본<sp/>통계는<sp/>시작<sp/>커밋을<sp/>포함한<sp/>범위로<sp/>집계했다.<sp/>이<sp/>통계<sp/>문서를<sp/>추가하는<sp/>후속<sp/>커밋은<sp/>집계<sp/>대상에서<sp/>제외한다.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">##<sp/>2.<sp/>커밋<sp/>수</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">|<sp/>기준<sp/>|<sp/>커밋<sp/>수<sp/>|</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">|---|---:|</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">|<sp/>시작<sp/>커밋<sp/>포함<sp/>전체<sp/>|<sp/>114<sp/>|</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">|<sp/>시작<sp/>커밋<sp/>이후만<sp/>|<sp/>113<sp/>|</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">|<sp/>코드<sp/>/<sp/>샘플<sp/>/<sp/>테스트를<sp/>건드린<sp/>커밋<sp/>|<sp/>83<sp/>|</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">|<sp/>문서를<sp/>건드린<sp/>커밋<sp/>|<sp/>86<sp/>|</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">|<sp/>문서만<sp/>변경한<sp/>커밋<sp/>|<sp/>31<sp/>|</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">범위<sp/>안<sp/>커밋<sp/>제목과<sp/>변경<sp/>파일은<sp/>모두<sp/>TextVisualizer<sp/>설계,<sp/>구현,<sp/>테스트,<sp/>샘플,<sp/>성능<sp/>분석에<sp/>해당한다.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">##<sp/>3.<sp/>최종<sp/>diff<sp/>기준<sp/>변화량</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">최종<sp/>diff<sp/>기준<sp/>변화량은<sp/>시작<sp/>커밋<sp/>직전<sp/>상태와<sp/>통계<sp/>산출<sp/>시점<sp/>최신<sp/>구현<sp/>커밋<sp/>상태를<sp/>비교한<sp/>값이다.<sp/>중간<sp/>커밋에서<sp/>추가했다가<sp/>다시<sp/>수정하거나<sp/>삭제한<sp/>line<sp/>churn은<sp/>중복<sp/>계산하지<sp/>않는다.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">|<sp/>범위<sp/>|<sp/>추가<sp/>|<sp/>삭제<sp/>|<sp/>순증<sp/>|<sp/>총<sp/>변화<sp/>|</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">|---|---:|---:|---:|---:|</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">|<sp/>전체<sp/>|<sp/>32,427<sp/>|<sp/>2<sp/>|<sp/>32,425<sp/>|<sp/>32,429<sp/>|</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">|<sp/>코드<sp/>/<sp/>샘플<sp/>/<sp/>테스트<sp/>(`docs/`<sp/>제외)<sp/>|<sp/>18,643<sp/>|<sp/>2<sp/>|<sp/>18,641<sp/>|<sp/>18,645<sp/>|</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">|<sp/>문서<sp/>(`docs/`)<sp/>|<sp/>13,784<sp/>|<sp/>0<sp/>|<sp/>13,784<sp/>|<sp/>13,784<sp/>|</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">코드<sp/>변화량만<sp/>볼<sp/>때는<sp/>`docs/`<sp/>제외<sp/>기준인<sp/>순증<sp/>`18,641`<sp/>line을<sp/>대표값으로<sp/>보면<sp/>된다.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">##<sp/>4.<sp/>영역별<sp/>최종<sp/>diff</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">|<sp/>영역<sp/>|<sp/>추가<sp/>|<sp/>삭제<sp/>|<sp/>순증<sp/>|<sp/>총<sp/>변화<sp/>|</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">|---|---:|---:|---:|---:|</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">|<sp/>`dali-ui-foundation/`<sp/>|<sp/>6,708<sp/>|<sp/>0<sp/>|<sp/>6,708<sp/>|<sp/>6,708<sp/>|</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">|<sp/>`automated-tests/`<sp/>|<sp/>4,225<sp/>|<sp/>0<sp/>|<sp/>4,225<sp/>|<sp/>4,225<sp/>|</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">|<sp/>`samples/`<sp/>|<sp/>7,710<sp/>|<sp/>2<sp/>|<sp/>7,708<sp/>|<sp/>7,712<sp/>|</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">|<sp/>`docs/`<sp/>|<sp/>13,784<sp/>|<sp/>0<sp/>|<sp/>13,784<sp/>|<sp/>13,784<sp/>|</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">현재<sp/>최종<sp/>diff에<sp/>남아<sp/>있는<sp/>변경<sp/>파일<sp/>수는<sp/>총<sp/>58개다.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">|<sp/>범위<sp/>|<sp/>파일<sp/>수<sp/>|</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">|---|---:|</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">|<sp/>전체<sp/>|<sp/>58<sp/>|</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">|<sp/>코드<sp/>/<sp/>샘플<sp/>/<sp/>테스트<sp/>(`docs/`<sp/>제외)<sp/>|<sp/>33<sp/>|</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">|<sp/>문서<sp/>(`docs/`)<sp/>|<sp/>25<sp/>|</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">##<sp/>5.<sp/>커밋별<sp/>누적<sp/>churn</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">커밋별<sp/>누적<sp/>churn은<sp/>각<sp/>커밋의<sp/>`--numstat`을<sp/>모두<sp/>합산한<sp/>값이다.<sp/>같은<sp/>줄을<sp/>여러<sp/>커밋에서<sp/>반복<sp/>수정하면<sp/>그만큼<sp/>여러<sp/>번<sp/>계산되므로,<sp/>실제<sp/>최종<sp/>코드<sp/>증가량보다<sp/>크다.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">|<sp/>범위<sp/>|<sp/>추가<sp/>|<sp/>삭제<sp/>|<sp/>순증<sp/>|<sp/>누적<sp/>변경<sp/>|</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">|---|---:|---:|---:|---:|</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">|<sp/>전체<sp/>|<sp/>35,836<sp/>|<sp/>3,411<sp/>|<sp/>32,425<sp/>|<sp/>39,247<sp/>|</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">|<sp/>코드<sp/>/<sp/>샘플<sp/>/<sp/>테스트<sp/>(`docs/`<sp/>제외)<sp/>|<sp/>20,043<sp/>|<sp/>1,402<sp/>|<sp/>18,641<sp/>|<sp/>21,445<sp/>|</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">|<sp/>문서<sp/>(`docs/`)<sp/>|<sp/>15,793<sp/>|<sp/>2,009<sp/>|<sp/>13,784<sp/>|<sp/>17,802<sp/>|</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">최종<sp/>결과물의<sp/>규모를<sp/>설명할<sp/>때는<sp/>최종<sp/>diff<sp/>기준을<sp/>사용하고,<sp/>개발<sp/>과정에서<sp/>실제로<sp/>어느<sp/>정도<sp/>수정이<sp/>오갔는지를<sp/>설명할<sp/>때는<sp/>누적<sp/>churn<sp/>기준을<sp/>사용한다.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">##<sp/>6.<sp/>집계<sp/>명령</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">대표<sp/>집계<sp/>명령은<sp/>다음과<sp/>같다.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">```sh</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">git<sp/>rev-list<sp/>--count<sp/>9970ed2009b9650167398ba5fc935a6d94a84f1f^..82f4977551c0034412faf9f17f205f107b73d57a</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">git<sp/>rev-list<sp/>--count<sp/>9970ed2009b9650167398ba5fc935a6d94a84f1f..82f4977551c0034412faf9f17f205f107b73d57a</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">git<sp/>diff<sp/>--numstat<sp/>9970ed2009b9650167398ba5fc935a6d94a84f1f^..82f4977551c0034412faf9f17f205f107b73d57a</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">git<sp/>log<sp/>--numstat<sp/>--format=<sp/>9970ed2009b9650167398ba5fc935a6d94a84f1f^..82f4977551c0034412faf9f17f205f107b73d57a</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">```</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">`docs/`<sp/>제외<sp/>통계는<sp/>`awk`에서<sp/>path<sp/>prefix가<sp/>`docs/`가<sp/>아닌<sp/>항목만<sp/>합산했다.</highlight></codeline>
